            "title": "盤中速報 - 方土昶(6265)大跌8.06%，報17.1元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>方土昶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6265:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6265\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6265-TW</a>)20日10:25股價下跌1.5元，報17.1元，跌幅8.06%，成交2,031張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>方土昶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6265:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6265\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6265-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子通路業，主要業務為電子零件買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲5.08%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.68%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+2,103 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,745 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+358 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,520 張</li> <li>融券增減：+71 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
